{"tid":545276,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講野講得太快可以點改善","createTime":"2018-01-30T11:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T11:45:59.000Z","uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c1f9cbce57f453dbc0d274903a346e725f2de2","tid":545276,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"一直以來講野都講得好快<br />\n無論係present，教補習，平時講野都好<br />\n成日都一輪嘴咁講晒啲野出黎<br />\nProf/補習學生成日都叫我講慢啲，話跟唔到<br />\n每次講野之前都會提自己講慢D<br />\n但慢咗一陣之後又會再快番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟有咩方法可以改善到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32712701f1173ccd2761a91bd5dbfe879aee8cd","tid":545276,"uid":16871,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:06:33.000Z","msg":"講慢啲"},{"pid":"5f47bef9c9285b12e7ea5f709bc94def3c653138","tid":545276,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"放粒釘係口先講野"},{"pid":"72f910b483b8a6dd4022053d1897f6c4bcb8c2ab","tid":545276,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯有逼自己諗野快d，等自己每次講野都可以同時分心tune自己既速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2bedf9ff4f135271570575c0450ff089f03062","tid":545276,"uid":12503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"試下講野前加發語詞<br />\n例如：「即係咁」、「係呢，有冇聽過...」之類，習慣講嘅時候慢啲每隻字都講清楚<br />\n<br />\n基於慣性，成句句子嘅語速會比較相近發語詞嘅速度"},{"pid":"4f4040f071e333aa8f2f0378820835dacf5ad156","tid":545276,"uid":79137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"用其他語言講野"},{"pid":"15a130bf03aadf6a7a3aba93500351cd7cedbfca","tid":545276,"uid":69168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"講野快唔係問題，<br />\n講野冇重點先係問題，<br />\n我老細講野又係好快，<br />\n不過就廢話多過重點，<br />\n每次聽佢講野好似做listening咁，<br />\n要撈返個重點出黎，<br />\n明明兩三句就應該講完"}]}